title: 10/02: Waiver Wire, Bell is Back! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Who are our top priorities on the Waiver Wire this week (2:00)? You know T.J. Yeldon will be one of them, but don't forget about the TEN DST and a bunch of WRs who are widely available. We're also reacting to Le'Veon Bell's return (5:45), discussing some players who are about 80% owned but may be available in your leagues (13:04) and giving you a sneak peak at the Waiver Wire options at each position (15:00) before expanding later in the show ... Recapping KC-DEN (29:50) and BAL-PIT (32:18) before we get the Dropometer out (36:30) ... Waiver Wire QBs (41:03) including Blake Bortles and Derek Carr, RBs (44:35) including Nyheim Hines and Tarik Cohen, WRs (48:55) including Chester Rogers and Taywan Taylor, TEs (54:45) including Vance McDonald and Cameron Brate, DSTs (58:30) and Kickers ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
